org.aksw.cubeqa.property

Class ComponentProperty

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.aksw.cubeqa.property.ComponentProperty
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ComponentProperty
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a component property of a RDF Data Cube. Implements the Multiton Pattern, with the key being the combination of cube name and uri, because information about values is safed. Immutable except for the labels.
